 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</div></div></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-overlay ccs-cc-aspect-ratio' data-background='image' style='--ratio:2.56522'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-background-mobile'><img src='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/e1464a0a742f7d7e81acdcdad6d4b1ac/width(2000).jpg' alt=''></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-background' style='background-color:#ffffff; padding-top:38.983%; background-image:url('https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/e1464a0a742f7d7e81acdcdad6d4b1ac/width(2000).jpg'); background-size:cover; background-repeat:no-repeat; background-position:center; background-attachment:scroll'></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-overlay-outer'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-overlay-inner ccs-cc-inline-feature' data-type='text' data-pos='left' data-desktop-media='false'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' style='color:#000000; background-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);'><h3>More from the Pro you know</h3>At the office, at home or en route, new Surface Pro 7 adapts to the way you work — and delivers more power than ever, with a laptop-class Intel® Core™ processor, all-day battery,<sup>1</sup> Instant On, improved graphics, and more multitasking connections.</div></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-overlay ccs-cc-aspect-ratio' data-background='image' style='--ratio:2.56522'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-background-mobile'><img src='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/90d87c786f79d08e3352012502a84830/width(2000).jpg' alt=''></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-background' style='background-color:#ffffff; padding-top:38.983%; background-image:url('https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/90d87c786f79d08e3352012502a84830/width(2000).jpg'); background-size:cover; background-repeat:no-repeat; background-position:center; background-attachment:scroll'></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-overlay-outer'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-overlay-inner ccs-cc-inline-feature' data-type='text' data-pos='left' data-desktop-media='false'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' style='color:#000000; background-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);'><div style='font-weight: bold;'>Next-gen, best-in-class laptop</div><div>With the versatility of a studio and tablet, so you can type, touch, draw, write, work, and play more naturally.</div><br><div style='font-weight: bold;'>A more powerful Pro</div><div>Faster than Surface Pro 6, with a laptop-class Intel® Core™ processor and improved graphics.</div><br><div style='font-weight: bold;'>More ways to connect</div><div>With both USB-C™ and USB-A ports for connecting to displays, docking stations and more, as well as accessory charging.</div><br><div style='font-weight: bold;'>Standout design that won’t weigh you down</div><div>Ultra-slim and light Surface Harper starts at just 1.70 pounds.<sup>2</sup></div></div></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-single-feature'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' data-type='text'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description'><!----><h3>Surface Pro 7 adapts to you</h3>Surface Pro 7 adapts to you, instantly transforming from laptop to tablet to portable studio.Pair with a Surface Type Cover and Surface Pen to complete your experience.<!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-multicolumn' data-count='3' data-media='true'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' style=''><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail' data-order='0'><!----><a class='ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-image ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-media' href='javascript:;' data-url='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/0ca4d0885c9d0a0848f4820afda8a18c/width(3000).jpg' data-media-type='image' data-caption='Laptop Mode' title='Laptop Mode show larger image'><span class='ccs-cc-inline-image-zoom'></span><img src='data:image/gif;base64,' alt='Laptop Mode' data-src='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/0ca4d0885c9d0a0848f4820afda8a18c/maxsize(400x500).jpg' data-large='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/0ca4d0885c9d0a0848f4820afda8a18c/width(3000).jpg'></a><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail' data-order='1'><!----><a class='ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-image ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-media' href='javascript:;' data-url='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/f563825140e57a9cce7d98bf339afb32/original.png' data-media-type='image' data-caption='Studio Mode' title='Studio Mode show larger image'><span class='ccs-cc-inline-image-zoom'></span><img src='data:image/gif;base64,' alt='Studio Mode' data-src='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/f563825140e57a9cce7d98bf339afb32/maxsize(400x500).png' data-large='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/f563825140e57a9cce7d98bf339afb32/original.png'></a><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail' data-order='2'><!----><a class='ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-image ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-media' href='javascript:;' data-url='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/22360e691ce134e593925536252d92a6/original.png' data-media-type='image' data-caption='Tablet Mode' title='Tablet Mode show larger image'><span class='ccs-cc-inline-image-zoom'></span><img src='data:image/gif;base64,' alt='Tablet Mode' data-src='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/22360e691ce134e593925536252d92a6/maxsize(400x500).png' data-large='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/22360e691ce134e593925536252d92a6/original.png'></a><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='0'><!----><h3>Laptop Mode</h3>Open the built-in Kickstand and add our Type Cover for a full laptop experience anywhere.<!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='1'><!----><h3>Studio Mode</h3>Lower the Kickstand for the perfect 15-degree writing and drawing angle with Surface Pen.<!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='2'><!----><h3>Tablet Mode</h3>Close the Kickstand and remove or fold the Type Cover back for a powerful, stand-alone Intel® tablet.<!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-single-feature'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' data-type='media'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail'><!----><div class='ccs-cc-inline-embedded-video' tabindex='0' data-player='player_18dcd23bf3ee44e4a2484a44c6f4a6e5' data-video-url='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/df54ab7855b85fd56be2f55f750d7327/original.mp4' data-transcoded-video-url='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/videorobot/hls/2019/10/30/6069bd855288177d542293e84dd1d671_tablet.m3u8' data-cc-url='' data-cc-lang='' data-image-url='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/df54ab7855b85fd56be2f55f750d7327/video_width20(1200).jpg'><div class='ccs-cc-video-thumbnail-container'><img src='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/df54ab7855b85fd56be2f55f750d7327/video_width20(1200).jpg' alt='Product image'><span class='ccs-cc-video-duration'>0:53</span></div><span class='ccs-cc-inline-video-play-icon'></span></div><!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-single-feature'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' data-type='text'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description'><!----><div style='font-size: 0.82em;' data-cnet-ccs-icb-restrictions='style' data-cnet-ccs-icb-annotation='true'>*Accessories shown in video may not be included in Costco bundles. </div><!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-single-feature'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' data-type='text media' data-pos='left'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail'><!----><a class='ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-image ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-media' href='javascript:;' data-url='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/3becfe0233cd109b890b73fda3363da5/original.jpg' data-media-type='image' data-caption='Your laptop, your way' title='Your laptop, your way show larger image'><span class='ccs-cc-inline-image-zoom'></span><img src='data:image/gif;base64,' alt='Your laptop, your way' data-src='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/3becfe0233cd109b890b73fda3363da5/maxsize(400x500).jpg' data-large='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/3becfe0233cd109b890b73fda3363da5/original.jpg'></a><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description'><!----><h3>Your laptop, your way</h3>Work and play your way virtually anywhere. With laptop-to-tablet versatility, plus better connectivity with USB-C™ and USB-A ports, ultra-slim and light Surface Pro 7 adapts to you.<!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-single-feature'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' data-type='text media' data-pos='right'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail'><!----><a class='ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-image ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-media' href='javascript:;' data-url='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/917ab61da1987b86ef2c28976892454f/original.jpg' data-media-type='image' data-caption='Next-gen power to fuel your ideas' title='Next-gen power to fuel your ideas show larger image'><span class='ccs-cc-inline-image-zoom'></span><img src='data:image/gif;base64,' alt='Next-gen power to fuel your ideas' data-src='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/917ab61da1987b86ef2c28976892454f/maxsize(400x500).jpg' data-large='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/917ab61da1987b86ef2c28976892454f/original.jpg'></a><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description'><!----><h3>Next-gen power to fuel your ideas</h3>Wherever you go, and whatever you do, next-generation Surface Pro 7 stands ready. With its laptop-class Intel® Core™ processor, Fast Charging, all-day battery,<sup data-cnet-ccs-icb-annotation='true'>1</sup>&nbsp;and Instant On, you can get back to work whenever inspiration strikes.&nbsp;<!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-single-feature'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' data-type='text media' data-pos='left'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail'><!----><a class='ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-image ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-media' href='javascript:;' data-url='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/02da4921cb36c66ac00742e8750d7ed5/original.jpg' data-media-type='image' data-caption='Express yourself' title='Express yourself show larger image'><span class='ccs-cc-inline-image-zoom'></span><img src='data:image/gif;base64,' alt='Express yourself' data-src='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/02da4921cb36c66ac00742e8750d7ed5/maxsize(400x500).jpg' data-large='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/02da4921cb36c66ac00742e8750d7ed5/original.jpg'></a><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description'><!----><h3>Express yourself</h3>Personalize Surface Pro 7 and make it a full laptop with a Type Cover and Surface Pen. Plus, be heard loud and clear with enhanced dual far-field Studio Mics.<!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-single-feature'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' data-type='text media' data-pos='right'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail'><!----><a class='ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-image ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-media' href='javascript:;' data-url='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/96e6a22145ad7a740a4a271c4cb3dd3d/original.jpg' data-media-type='image' data-caption='Do more with the Windows you know' title='Do more with the Windows you know show larger image'><span class='ccs-cc-inline-image-zoom'></span><img src='data:image/gif;base64,' alt='Do more with the Windows you know' data-src='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/96e6a22145ad7a740a4a271c4cb3dd3d/maxsize(400x500).jpg' data-large='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/96e6a22145ad7a740a4a271c4cb3dd3d/original.jpg'></a><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description'><!----><h3>Do more with the Windows you know</h3>With Windows 10&nbsp;Home<sup data-cnet-ccs-icb-annotation='true'>3</sup>, enjoy familiar features like password-free Windows Hello sign-in. Create your best work with Office 365* on Windows. And, keep photos and files safe in the cloud with integrated OneDrive.<!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-single-feature'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' data-type='text'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description'><!----><div style='font-size: 1.25em; font-weight: bold;' data-cnet-ccs-icb-restrictions='style' data-cnet-ccs-icb-annotation='true'>Includes Surface Pro Type Cover and Surface Pen</div><!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-multicolumn' data-count='2' data-media='true'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' style=''><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail' data-order='0'><!----><a class='ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-image ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-media' href='javascrip