data-asset-url='/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/b57547cb-0275-4b54-93d1-223b860b0a03.jpg' data-asset-wrapper='rich-features' data-height='336' data-section-template-code='rich-features' data-width='480' height='336' module-id='dellbtoc' src='https://smedia.webcollage.net/rwvfp/wc/cp/1566476620260_a0970033-354a-4aa2-8dba-07038263fc20/module/dellbtoc/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/b57547cb-0275-4b54-93d1-223b860b0a03.jpg.w480.jpg' title='Dell Cinema: Experience less buffering, brilliant sound clarity, and an ultra-vivid picture' wcpc='1564092588085' width='480'> </div> </div> <div class='wc-text-wrap'><h3 class='wc-rich-content-header wc-feature-main-header '>Dell Cinema: Experience less buffering, brilliant sound clarity, and an ultra-vivid picture</h3> <div class='wc-rich-content-description'> <b>CinemaColor</b><br><b>BRING YOUR ENTERTAINMENT TO LIFE:</b> Best-in-class technology, paired with advanced hardware and software power content with incredible dynamic range.<br><br><b>CinemaSound<br></b><b>EPIC CINEMA SOUND THAT SURROUNDS YOU:</b> Deeper bass, greater volume, and 3D Sound with Waves MaxxAudio<sup>®</sup> Pro.<br><br><b>CinemaStream<br></b><b>DESIGNED TO BUFFER LESS AND BINGE MORE:&nbsp;</b>CinemaStream delivers smoother video streaming. </div> </div> </li> <li class='wc-rich-feature-item wc-text-placement-false wc-even-0 wc-has-media wc-thumb-medium '>  <div class='wc-media-wrap' style='width:480px !important'> <div class='wc-media-inner-wrap' style='max-width:480px !important'> <img alt='' class='wc-media wc-image' data-asset-title='Powerhouse performance' data-asset-type='image' data-asset-url='/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/5d18c7bb-030a-4ae1-89c6-ff7b73d0176c.jpg' data-asset-wrapper='rich-features' data-height='356' data-section-template-code='rich-features' data-width='480' height='356' module-id='dellbtoc' src='https://smedia.webcollage.net/rwvfp/wc/cp/1566476620260_a0970033-354a-4aa2-8dba-07038263fc20/module/dellbtoc/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/5d18c7bb-030a-4ae1-89c6-ff7b73d0176c.jpg.w480.jpg' title='Powerhouse performance' wcpc='1564092588085' width='480'> </div> </div> <div class='wc-text-wrap'><h3 class='wc-rich-content-header wc-feature-main-header '>Powerhouse performance</h3> <div class='wc-rich-content-description'> <b>Ultimate mobile performance:</b> The most powerful XPS laptop we’ve ever built includes the latest 9th Generation Intel<sup>®</sup> Core™ i9-9980HK processor with 8 cores, delivering the ultimate power for gamers and creators.<br><b><br>Less wait, more create:</b> The NVIDIA<sup>®</sup> GeForce<sup>®</sup> GTX 1650 GPU power accelerates your favorite creative apps for greater performance and faster speed in video editing, graphic design, photography, and game broadcasting. Supercharge your favorite games with the breakthrough graphics performance of the award-winning NVIDIA<sup>®&nbsp;</sup>Turing™ architecture. </div> </div> </li> <li class='wc-rich-feature-item wc-text-placement-false wc-odd-0 wc-has-media wc-thumb-medium '>  <div class='wc-media-wrap' style='width:480px !important'> <div class='wc-media-inner-wrap' style='max-width:480px !important'> <img alt='' class='wc-media wc-image' data-asset-title='Visualize the victory' data-asset-type='image' data-asset-url='/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/aced348c-9f18-4e92-9b34-38f8353a023d.png' data-asset-wrapper='rich-features' data-height='233' data-section-template-code='rich-features' data-width='480' height='233' module-id='dellbtoc' src='https://smedia.webcollage.net/rwvfp/wc/cp/1566476620260_a0970033-354a-4aa2-8dba-07038263fc20/module/dellbtoc/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/aced348c-9f18-4e92-9b34-38f8353a023d.png.w480.png' title='Visualize the victory' wcpc='1564092588085' width='480'> </div> </div> <div class='wc-text-wrap'><h3 class='wc-rich-content-header wc-feature-main-header '>Visualize the victory</h3> <div class='wc-rich-content-description'> See what your game is capable of with powerhouse, NVIDIA<sup>®</sup> GeForce<sup>®</sup> GTX 1650 graphics and 4GB GDDR5 dedicated memory With the new NVIDIA<sup>®</sup> GeForce<sup>®&nbsp;</sup>GTX graphics cards, your game graphics are even more realistic and immersive. Ray tracing simulates the true behavior of light for real-time, cinematic-quality rendering to the most visually intense games. </div> </div> </li> <li class='wc-rich-feature-item wc-text-placement-true wc-even-0 wc-has-media wc-thumb-large '>  <div class='wc-media-wrap'> <div class='wc-media-inner-wrap'> <img alt='' class='wc-media wc-image' data-asset-title='Meet 15.6-inch performance laptop' data-asset-type='image' data-asset-url='/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/87d5b087-84db-436f-ad06-3096b3329cbf.png' data-asset-wrapper='rich-features' data-height='364' data-section-template-code='rich-features' data-width='1004' height='364' module-id='dellbtoc' src='https://smedia.webcollage.net/rwvfp/wc/cp/1566476620260_a0970033-354a-4aa2-8dba-07038263fc20/module/dellbtoc/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/87d5b087-84db-436f-ad06-3096b3329cbf.png.w1920.png' title='Meet 15.6-inch performance laptop' wcpc='1564092588085' width='1004'> </div> </div> <div class='wc-text-wrap'><h3 class='wc-rich-content-header wc-feature-main-header '>Meet 15.6-inch performance laptop</h3> <div class='wc-rich-content-description'> <b>Improved camera location:&nbsp;</b>We pushed innovation to its limits to create the our smallest HD webcam that’s housed in the top of the famed InfinityEdge display—now front and center.<br><b><br>Revolutionary webcam construction:</b> The new XPS 15 webcam isn't just smaller—it's also better. A new 4-element lens uses more elements than a typical webcam to deliver sharp video in all areas of the frame, while temporal noise reduction uses advanced noise reduction, significantly improving video quality, especially in dim lighting conditions. Finally, the lens is assembled with precise machinery to ensure all points of the image are in focus.<br><b><br></b> </div> </div> </li> <li class='wc-rich-feature-item wc-text-placement-false wc-odd-0 wc-has-media wc-thumb-medium '>  <div class='wc-media-wrap' style='width:480px !important'> <div class='wc-media-inner-wrap' style='max-width:480px !important'> <img alt='' class='wc-media wc-image' data-asset-title='Maximum memory and storage' data-asset-type='image' data-asset-url='/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/4612126a-f1c6-4b35-94bf-cb1570635329.jpg' data-asset-wrapper='rich-features' data-height='273' data-section-template-code='rich-features' data-width='480' height='273' module-id='dellbtoc' src='https://smedia.webcollage.net/rwvfp/wc/cp/1566476620260_a0970033-354a-4aa2-8dba-07038263fc20/module/dellbtoc/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/4612126a-f1c6-4b35-94bf-cb1570635329.jpg.w480.jpg' title='Maximum memory and storage' wcpc='1564092588085' width='480'> </div> </div> <div class='wc-text-wrap'><h3 class='wc-rich-content-header wc-feature-main-header '>Maximum memory and storage</h3> <div class='wc-rich-content-description'> Supports 32GB of memory with a bandwidth of 2666MHz, 1.2 times the speed of 2133MHz. Faster memory means you get to the content that you need quicker. Storage of 1TB solid state drive, available in faster PCIe versions, provide plenty of storage room and high-performance responsiveness to access and run your applications quickly. The XPS 15 boots and resumes in seconds with a solid state drive, so you can do more without waiting.<br><br><b>Killer™ Wireless:&nbsp;</b>Featuring advanced Wi-Fi 6 technology and theoretical throughput speeds of 2.4 Gbps, the Killer AX1650 is nearly 3 times as fast as the previous generation of 80MHz 2x2 AC products. The Killer 1650 automatically detects, classifies, and prioritizes streaming video, communication, and game traffic in your system for fast, smooth online experiences. </div> </div> </li> <li class='wc-rich-feature-item wc-text-placement-false wc-even-0 wc-has-media wc-thumb-medium '>  <div class='wc-media-wrap' style='width:480px !important'> <div class='wc-media-inner-wrap' style='max-width:480px !important'> <img alt='' class='wc-media wc-image' data-asset-title='InfinityEdge display' data-asset-type='image' data-asset-url='/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/f26535e4-09c6-4abc-ac65-caef87d09e31.jpg' data-asset-wrapper='rich-features' data-height='241' data-section-template-code='rich-features' data-width='480' height='241' module-id='dellbtoc' src='https://smedia.webcollage.net/rwvfp/wc/cp/1566476620260_a0970033-354a-4aa2-8dba-07038263fc20/module/dellbtoc/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/f26535e4-09c6-4abc-ac65-caef87d09e31.jpg.w480.jpg' title='InfinityEdge display' wcpc='1564092588085' width='480'> </div> </div> <div class='wc-text-wrap'><h3 class='wc-rich-content-header wc-feature-main-header '>InfinityEdge display</h3> <div class='wc-rich-content-description'> The virtually borderless display maximizes screen space by accommodating a 15.6-inch display inside a laptop closer to the size of a 14-inch, thanks to a bezel measuring just 6.04mm on the sides and 7.08mm on the top.<br><b><br>One-of-a-kind design:&nbsp;</b>Measuring in at a slim 11-17mm and starting at just 4 pounds (1.8 kg) with a solid state drive period. </div> </div> </li> <li class='wc-rich-feature-item wc-text-placement-false wc-odd-0 wc-has-media wc-thumb-medium '>  <div class='wc-media-wrap' style='width:480px !important'> <div class='wc-media-inner-wrap' style='max-width:480px !important'> <img alt='' class='wc-media wc-image' data-asset-title='A stunning view, wherever you go' data-asset-type='image' data-asset-url='/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/54d474db-2d3a-46c3-81c6-f3be585ba99f.jpg' data-asset-wrapper='rich-features' data-height='273' data-section-template-code='rich-features' data-width='480' height='273' module-id='dellbtoc' src='https://smedia.webcollage.net/rwvfp/wc/cp/1566476620260_a0970033-354a-4aa2-8dba-07038263fc20/module/dellbtoc/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/54d474db-2d3a-46c3-81c6-f3be585ba99f.jpg.w480.jpg' title='A stunning view, wherever you go' wcpc='1564092588085' width='480'> </div> </div> <div class='wc-text-wrap'><h3 class='wc-rich-content-header wc-feature-main-header '>A stunning view, wherever you go</h3> <div class='wc-rich-content-description'> <b>Dazzling detail:</b> With the UltraSharp 4K Ultra HD display (3840 x 2160), you can see each detail of every pixel without needing to zoom in. And with 6 million more pixels than Full HD and 3 million more than the MacBook Pro, you can edit images with pinpoint accuracy without worrying about blurriness or jagged lines.<br><b><br><br></b> </div> </div> </li> <li class='wc-rich-feature-item wc-text-placement-false wc-even-0 wc-has-media wc-thumb-medium '>  <div class='wc-media-wrap' style='width:480px !important'> <div class='wc-media-inner-wrap' style='max-width:480px !important'> <img alt='' class='wc-media wc-image' data-asset-title='100% Adobe RGB color' data-asset-type='image' data-asset-url='/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/8acd1198-e09e-4f09-904d-41b283f2525a.jpg' data-asset-wrapper='rich-features' data-height='305' data-section-template-code='rich-features' data-width='480' height='305' module-id='dellbtoc' src='https://smedia.webcollage.net/rwvfp/wc/cp/1566476620260_a0970033-354a-4aa2-8dba-07038263fc20/module/dellbtoc/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/8acd1198-e09e-4f09-904d-41b283f2525a.jpg.w480.jpg' title='100% Adobe RGB color' wcpc='1564092588085' width='480'> </div> </div> <div class='wc-text-wrap'><h3 class='wc-rich-content-header wc-feature-main-header '>100% Adobe RGB color</h3> <div class='wc-rich-content-description'> With 100% Adobe RGB color, the XPS 15 covers a wider color gamut and produces shades of color outside conventional panels so you can see more of what you see in real life. And with over 16 million colors, images appear smoother and color gradients are amazingly lifelike with more depth and dimension. Included is Dell PremierColor software, which automatically remaps content not already in Adobe RGB format for onscreen colors that appear amazingly accurate and true to life.<br><b><br>Beautiful from any angle:</b> The anti-reflective screen combined with superior 500-nit brightness on the UHD display frees you to enjoy your entertainment outdoors. Plus, the wide-viewing panel provides a wider viewing angle, so you can share your screen without missing a thing.<br><b><br>Touch friendly:&nbsp;</b>Tap, swipe and pinch your way around the screen. The touch display lets you interact naturally with your technology. </div> </div> </li> <li class='wc-rich-feature-item wc-text-placement-false wc-odd-0 wc-has-media wc-thumb-medium '>  <div class='wc-media-wrap' style='width:478px !important'> <div class='wc-media-inner-wrap' style='max-width:478px !important'> <img alt='' class='wc-media wc-image' data-asset-title='Interact intuitively' data-asset-type='image' data-asset-url='/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/716e71e2-6732-4b5c-b7a2-5f2f2a2745f4.JPG' data-asset-wrapper='rich-features' data-height='347' data-section-template-code='rich-features' data-width='478' height='347' module-id='dellbtoc' src='https://smedia.webcollage.net/rwvfp/wc/cp/1566476620260_a0970033-354a-4aa2-8dba-07038263fc20/module/dellbtoc/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/716e71e2-6732-4b5c-b7a2-5f2f2a2745f4.JPG.w1920.jpg' title='Interact intuitively' wcpc='1564092588085' width='478'> </div> </div> <div class='wc-text-wrap'><h3 class='wc-rich-content-header wc-feature-main-header '>Interact intuitively</h3> <div class='wc-rich-content-description'> <b>Pinch, zoom and click with confidence:&nbsp;</b>The precision touch pad prevents jumping and floating cursors, while Accidental Activation Prevention puts a stop to unintentional clicks when your palm hits the touch pad.<br><b><br>Windows Hello:&nbsp;</b>Enjoy a password-free sign-in with the fingerprint reader, which is integrated into the power button that gives you the fastest, most secure way to unlock your laptop. Using your finger, it recognizes you apart from all others. It waves you in with a friendly hello and even works on apps and Microsoft Edge websites. </div> </div> </li> <li class='wc-rich-feature-item wc-text-placement-false wc-even-0 wc-has-media wc-thumb-medium '>  <div class='wc-media-wrap' style='width:480px !important'> <div class='wc-media-inner-wrap' style='max-width:480px !important'> <img alt='' class='wc-media wc-image' data-asset-title='More environmentally responsible than ever' data-asset-type='image' data-asset-url='/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/88bc5e1f-f93d-412a-a269-ec857ca6a81b.jpg' data-asset-wrapper='rich-features' data-height='274' data-section-template-code='rich-features' data-width='480' height='274' module-id='dellbtoc' src='https://smedia.webcollage.net/rwvfp/wc/cp/1566476620260_a0970033-354a-4aa2-8dba-07038263fc20/module/dellbtoc/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/88bc5e1f-f93d-412a-a269-ec857ca6a81b.jpg.w480.jpg' title='More environmentally responsible than ever' wcpc='1564092588085' width='480'> </div> </div> <div class='wc-text-wrap'><h3 class='wc-rich-content-header wc-feature-main-header '>More environmentally responsible than ever</h3> <div class='wc-rich-content-description'> <b>Power-efficient:&nbsp;</b>XPS 15 is ENERGY STAR<sup>®&nbsp;</sup>qualified.<br><br><b>Smarter materials:</b> Free of materials like cadmium, mercury and some phthalates, it’s also EPEAT<sup>®</sup> registered and BFR/PVC-free.<br><br><b>Saving our seas:</b> Recognized by CES with a '2018 Best of Innovation Award,' our black packaging trays are a step beyond recycled. Twenty-five percent of the material consists of ocean plastics collected from coastal areas, while the remaining 75% is made up of other recycled plastics.<br><b><br>Recycle-friendly:&nbsp;</b>Over 90% of the laptop (by weight) can be easily recycled or reused. </div> </div> </li> <li class='wc-rich-feature-item wc-text-placement-false wc-odd-0 wc-has-media wc-thumb-medium wc-last '>  <div class='wc-media-wrap' style='width:480px !important'> <div class='wc-media-inner-wrap' style='max-width:480px !important'> <img alt='' class='wc-media wc-image' data-asset-title='Artfully constructed from premium materials' data-asset-type='image' data-asset-url='/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/ed0a0ef9-8148-47c5-bc74-1bbdc6ded136.jpg' data-asset-wrapper='rich-features' data-height='310' data-section-template-code='rich-features' data-width='480' height='310' module-id='dellbtoc' src='https://smedia.webcollage.net/rwvfp/wc/cp/1566476620260_a0970033-354a-4aa2-8dba-07038263fc20/module/dellbtoc/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-27761226-7f70-4fb8-a667-e3c0d9fea7da/ed0a0ef9-8148-47c5-bc74-1bbdc6ded136.jpg.w480.jpg' title='Artfully constructed from premium materials' wcpc='1564092588085' width='480'> </div> </div> <div class='wc-text-wrap'><h3 class='wc-rich-content-header wc-feature-main-header '>Artfully constructed from premium materials</h3> <div class='wc-rich-content-description'> <b>Maximum durability:&nbsp;</b>Cut with precision from a single block of aluminum for a sturdy, durable chassis in a beautiful design. The Corning<sup>®</sup> Gorilla<sup>®</sup> Glass 4 is twice as damage resistant compared to competitive products.<br><b><br>Cool under pressure:&nbsp;</b>The palm rest is made from carbon fiber. It's strong and thin like aluminum, but lighter and cooler to the touch. </div> </div> </li> </ul> </div></div><div class='wc-clear-both' style='height: 0px !important'></div></div><div class='wc-fragment wc-no-focus' data-channel-product-name='' data-compiler-v='2020.7.2.487' data-cpi='100524117' data-gtin='00884116316589' data-is-capdesc-open='false' data-language-code='en' data-module-brand='Dell' data-module-code='dellbtoc' data-module-name='DellBtoC US' data-mpn='XPS7590-9589SLV-PUS' data-prod-category='XPS7590-7473SLV-PUS' data-produced='2020-06-22 16:59' data-section-caption='Unite your devices with Dell Mobile Connect' data-section-tag='features' data-section-template-code='rich-features' data-vendor-name='XPS7590-9589SLV-PUS' data-wcpc='1564092588085' id='wc-features-c98b2624'><h2 class='wc-rich-features-center-984'>Unite your devices with Dell Mobile Connect</h2><div class='wc-aplus-body'><div class='wc-reset'> <ul class='wc-rich-features wc-rich-content-orientation-zigzag wc-first wc-last wc-no-line-seperator wc-rich-features-center-984'> <li class='wc-rich-feature-item wc-text-placement-true wc-odd-0 wc-first wc-has-media wc-thumb-medium wc-has-no-caption wc-last '> <div class='wc-media-wrap' style='width:480px !important'> <div class='wc-media-inner-wrap' style='max-width:480px !important'> <img alt='' class='wc-media wc-image' data-asset-type='image' data-asset-url='/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-1f3c318f-31b6-4252-9de9-fe88d6715409/432415a2-0928-4e8a-9e2d-f53c9bc3eb3b.PNG' data-asset-wrapper='rich-features' data-height='265' data-section-template-code='rich-features' data-width='480' height='265' module-id='dellbtoc' src='https://smedia.webcollage.net/rwvfp/wc/cp/1566476620260_a0970033-354a-4aa2-8dba-07038263fc20/module/dellbtoc/_cp/products/1564092588085/tab-1f3c318f-31b6-4252-9de9-fe88d6715409/432415a2-0928-4e8a-9e2d-f53c9bc3eb3b.PNG.w480.png' title='' wcpc='1564092588085' width='480'> </div> </div> <div class='wc-text-wrap'> <div class='wc-rich-content-description'> Dell Mobile Connect wirelessly integrates your smartphone with your PC, allowing you to make phone calls, send SMS, get notifications and interact with all of your favorite mobile apps right from your PC screen.<br><b><br>Seamless PC/smartphone integration:</b> Access multiple devices without dividing your attention—Dell Mobile Connect pairs your iOS or Android smartphone with your laptop.<br><b><br>Limit disruptions:</b> With Dell Mobile Connect, you get the option to channel notifications from phone calls, SMS, IMs and other apps right to your laptop. Keep your focus on a single screen and respond only when it’s convenient for you.<br><b><br>Maintain your privacy:</b> Your phone connects to your PC via Dell Mobile Connect’s point-to-point, secure connection so your data is never exposed via unsecure internet connections.<br><br>*Dell Mobile Connect App must be downloaded to your PC and smartphone. Interacting with mobile apps via mirroring available only on Android devices. </div> </div> </li> </ul> </div></div><div class='wc-clear-both' style='height: 0px !important'></div></div><div class='wc-fragment wc-no-focus' data-channel-product-name='' data-compiler-v='2020.7.2.487' data-cpi='100524117' data-gtin='00884116316589' data-is-capdesc-open='false' data-language-code='en' data-module-brand='Dell' data-module-code='dellbtoc' data-module-name='DellBtoC US' data-mpn='XPS7590-9589SLV-PUS' data-prod-category='XPS7590-7473SLV-PUS' data-produced='2020-06-22 16:59' data-section-caption='Ports &amp; Slots' data-section-tag='demo' data-section-template-code='tour' data-vendor-name='XPS7590-9589SLV-PUS' data-wcpc='1564092588085' id='wc-demo-b4de3b25'><h2>Ports &amp; Slots</h2><div class='wc-aplus-body'><div class='wc-tour-container wc-tour-outer' data-resources-base='https://smedia.webcollage.net/rwvfp/wc/cp/1566476620260_a0970033-354a-4aa2-8dba-07038263fc20/module/dellbtoc/'> <div class='wc-jso