redirect/021f18cd2284319382a19c53460c0f90/original.jpg'></a><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description'><!----><h3>New ways to connect</h3>Getting into your flow and making connections is easier than ever on Surface Laptop 3, with multitasking USB-C™ and USB-A ports, interactive touchscreen, enhanced Studio Mics and wake on open.<!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-single-feature'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' data-type='text media' data-pos='right'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail'><!----><a class='ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-image ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-media' href='javascript:;' data-url='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/466ea7bdd6245ed53a041cb0512ed952/original.jpg' data-media-type='image' data-caption='Do more with the Windows you know' title='Do more with the Windows you know show larger image'><span class='ccs-cc-inline-image-zoom'></span><img src='data:image/gif;base64,' alt='Do more with the Windows you know' data-src='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/466ea7bdd6245ed53a041cb0512ed952/maxsize(400x500).jpg' data-large='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/466ea7bdd6245ed53a041cb0512ed952/original.jpg'></a><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description'><!----><h3>Do more with the Windows you know</h3>Get started right away with the Windows you know,<sup data-cnet-ccs-icb-annotation='true'>2</sup> including password-free Windows Hello sign-in. Browse faster with Microsoft Edge, keep your content safe in the cloud with integrated OneDrive, and create your best work with Office 365.<!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-single-feature'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' data-type='text media' data-pos='right'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail'><!----><