a-pos='left'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail'><!----><a class='ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-image ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-media' href='javascript:;' data-url='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/d469bff164ee9ae295a848f8be7426b9/original.jpg' data-media-type='image' data-caption='Thin, light, and always connected' title='Thin, light, and always connected show larger image'><span class='ccs-cc-inline-image-zoom'></span><img src='data:image/gif;base64,' alt='Thin, light, and always connected' data-src='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/d469bff164ee9ae295a848f8be7426b9/maxsize(400x500).jpg' data-large='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/d469bff164ee9ae295a848f8be7426b9/original.jpg'></a><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description'><!----><h3>Thin, light, and always connected</h3>Connect nearly anywhere, any time with friends, family, or on a high-priority project. Blazing-fast LTE<sup data-cnet-ccs-icb-annotation='true'>1</sup> keeps you connected so you can finish an email on the go or easily access your files and photos with OneDrive.<!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-single-feature'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' data-type='text media' data-pos='right'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail'><!----><a class='ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-image ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-media' href='javascript:;' data-url='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaserverredirect/127586eb71e65a36cc0907c1c4ebaa13/original.jpg' data-media-type='image' data-caption='Built for Windows 10 and web-first experiences' title='Built for Windows 10 and web-first experiences show larger image'><span class='ccs-cc-inline-image-zoom'></span><img src='data:image/gif;base64,' alt='Built for Windows 10 and web-first experiences' data-src='https://cdn.cnetcontent.com/syndication/mediaser