e-multicolumn' data-count='2' data-media='true'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' style=''><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail' data-order='0'><!----><img src='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/0/C/F/B/7/0CFB75F60E35D3C465331CD66BD3045D3AF0DED1_i_75_featurtn.jpg' alt='Responsive and reliable performance' data-large='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/0/C/F/B/7/0CFB75F60E35D3C465331CD66BD3045D3AF0DED1_i_75_featurtn.jpg'><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail' data-order='1'><!----><a class='ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-image ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-media ccs-cc-inline-clickable' href='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/B/4/6/0/9/B4609D1B7405CFC5C1435E3CC6C576C1275DE301_feature.jpg' data-media-type='image' data-caption='Sleek. Stylish. Powerful.' title='Sleek. Stylish. Powerful. show larger image'><span class='ccs-cc-inline-image-zoom'></span><img src='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/B/4/6/0/9/B4609D1B7405CFC5C1435E3CC6C576C1275DE301_i_75_featurtn.jpg' alt='Sleek. Stylish. Powerful.' data-large='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/B/4/6/0/9/B4609D1B7405CFC5C1435E3CC6C576C1275DE301_feature.jpg'></a><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='0'><!----><h3>Responsive and reliable performance</h3>A laptop with the power to surf, stream,<sup><a id='ccs-f2inline-c67693' href='#ccs-ft2inline-c67693'>2</a></sup> and do so much more with an AMD processor<sup><a id='ccs-f1inline-c67693' href='#ccs-ft1inline-c67693'>1</a></sup>. Plus extensive quality testing ensures that you can keep going...and going.<!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='1'><!----><h3>Sleek. Stylish. Powerful.</h3>A sleek and stylish design makes this eye-catching laptop easy to take anywhere. With its beautiful brushed keyboard and color-matched hinge, the smartly designed HP 17' laptop looks as good as it performs.<!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-multicolumn' data-count='2' data-media='true'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' style=''><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail' data-order='0'><!----><img src='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/D/B/F/D/4/DBFD4BEAC924DAD94470301B66E2E20E0DBB5DF6_i_75_featurtn.jpg' alt='Stay Connected and Entertained' data-large='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/D/B/F/D/4/DBFD4BEAC924DAD94470301B66E2E20E0DBB5DF6_i_75_featurtn.jpg'><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='0'><!----><h3>Stay Connected and Entertained</h3>Stay connected and entertained with a long-lasting HP Fast charge battery and visually rich display. Plus, easily store and enjoy your favorite music, movies, and photos with ample storage.<!----></div></div></div><h2>Key Features</h2><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-multicolumn' data-count='2' data-media='true'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' style=''><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail' data-order='0'><!----><img src='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/5/8/B/9/D/58B9D45B2206D56245D41505E396C76B1D3EF9EA_i_75_featurtn.jpg' alt='Windows 10' data-large='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/5/8/B/9/D/58B9D45B2206D56245D41505E396C76B1D3EF9EA_i_75_featurtn.jpg'><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail' data-order='1'><!----><img src='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/C/3/A/1/4/C3A1489CC04700BEBBA095643F7B182AC36E4BBA_i_75_featurtn.jpg' alt='AMD Ryzen<sup>™</sup> 5 processor' data-large='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/C/3/A/1/4/C3A1489CC04700BEBBA095643F7B182AC36E4BBA_i_75_featurtn.jpg'><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='0'><!----><h3>Windows 10</h3>Do great things confidently with the familiar feel of Windows - only better.<!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='1'><!----><h3>AMD Ryzen<sup>™</sup> 5 processor</h3>Tap into truly impressive notebook performance. A revolutionary new architecture with amazing battery life that delivers exceptional multi-threaded processing and Vega graphics for intensive multimedia tasks.<!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-multicolumn' data-count='2' data-media='true'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' style=''><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail' data-order='0'><!----><img src='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/F/D/7/B/1/FD7B17B398CCA5F7FBA3E3568F34F11092583392_i_75_featurtn.jpg' alt='Hard drive storage' data-large='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/F/D/7/B/1/FD7B17B398CCA5F7FBA3E3568F34F11092583392_i_75_featurtn.jpg'><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail' data-order='1'><!----><img src='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/E/1/E/5/2/E1E524C1DB99B2004B6677ED0542AB067AA458DC_i_75_featurtn.jpg' alt='HD+ touchscreen' data-large='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/E/1/E/5/2/E1E524C1DB99B2004B6677ED0542AB067AA458DC_i_75_featurtn.jpg'><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='0'><!----><h3>Hard drive storage</h3>Don’t worry about growing your collection of digital movies, songs, and pictures. With massive storage options you can save it all, and still have plenty of room left over.<!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='1'><!----><h3>HD+ touchscreen</h3>Experience your visuals in crisp quality and intuitively control your PC right from the screen. The 1600 x 900 resolution delivers 1.4 million pixels, 40% more than normal HD, for boosted definition.<!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-multicolumn' data-count='2' data-media='true'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' style=''><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail' data-order='0'><!----><img src='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/_STD/px/px.gif' alt='AMD Radeon<sup>™</sup> Vega graphics' data-large='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/_STD/px/px.gif'><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail' data-order='1'><!----><img src='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/F/4/0/E/2/F40E268CB243F9CD1549F12B5D4BDC7304E10339_i_75_featurtn.jpg' alt='DDR4 RAM' data-large='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/F/4/0/E/2/F40E268CB243F9CD1549F12B5D4BDC7304E10339_i_75_featurtn.jpg'><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='0'><!----><h3>AMD Radeon<sup>™</sup> Vega graphics</h3>Thrill your visual senses with the latest AMD graphics compute engines for fast, powerful, and fluid graphics. Combine with the latest multimedia for incredible performance.<!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='1'><!----><h3>DDR4 RAM</h3>Designed to run more efficiently and more reliably at faster speeds, DDR4 is the future of RAM. With its higher bandwidth, everything from multi-tasking to playing games gets a performance boost.<!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-multicolumn' data-count='2' data-media='true'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' style=''><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail' data-order='0'><!----><img src='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/5/D/4/7/D/5D47D66E083A3EB44A0BDFE89531C27D6EADC618_i_75_featurtn.jpg' alt='802.11 a/c (1x1) WLAN &amp; Bluetooth<sup>®</sup> 4.2' data-large='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/5/D/4/7/D/5D47D66E083A3EB44A0BDFE89531C27D6EADC618_i_75_featurtn.jpg'><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail' data-order='1'><!----><img src='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/5/A/5/A/9/5A5A9926A61EDAB4DC7683EE77EC0DD680EE295B_i_75_featurtn.jpg' alt='USB 3.1 connector' data-large='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/5/A/5/A/9/5A5A9926A61EDAB4DC7683EE77EC0DD680EE295B_i_75_featurtn.jpg'><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='0'><!----><h3>802.11 a/c (1x1) WLAN &amp; Bluetooth<sup>®</sup> 4.2</h3>Stay connected to Wi-Fi and to Bluetooth<sup>®</sup> accessories with wireless technology.<!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='1'><!----><h3>USB 3.1 connector</h3>With the world’s most popular USB connection, you can easily connect any of your existing USB devices and experience data transfer speeds ten times faster than USB 2.0.<!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-multicolumn' data-count='2' data-media='true'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' style=''><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail' data-order='0'><!----><img src='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/3/9/1/5/3/3915327F585184750542E492774E25323ACFBD8D_i_75_featurtn.jpg' alt='Dual front-facing speakers' data-large='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/3/9/1/5/3/3915327F585184750542E492774E25323ACFBD8D_i_75_featurtn.jpg'><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail' data-order='1'><!----><a class='ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-image ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail-media ccs-cc-inline-clickable' href='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/9/A/2/D/E/9A2DECE3628588681C3EE0492E9FE838695C3704_feature.jpg' data-media-type='image' data-caption='HP TrueVision HD Camera' title='HP TrueVision HD Camera show larger image'><span class='ccs-cc-inline-image-zoom'></span><img src='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/9/A/2/D/E/9A2DECE3628588681C3EE0492E9FE838695C3704_i_75_featurtn.jpg' alt='HP TrueVision HD Camera' data-large='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/9/A/2/D/E/9A2DECE3628588681C3EE0492E9FE838695C3704_feature.jpg'></a><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='0'><!----><h3>Dual front-facing speakers</h3>Pump up the volume to your favorite music, movie or game. When your audio is directed towards you, nothing comes between you and your entertainment.<!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='1'><!----><h3>HP TrueVision HD Camera</h3>Video chat in vibrant clarity, even in low light and make every conversation a face-to-face experience for a better way to stay in touch.<!----></div></div></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-features-block ccs-cc-inline-multicolumn' data-count='2' data-media='true'><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature' style=''><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail' data-order='0'><!----><img src='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/3/0/6/8/6/306866B8312DA76067BDFF396B3F4D7FAA5A7FDE_i_75_featurtn.jpg' alt='Dropbox cloud storage' data-large='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/3/0/6/8/6/306866B8312DA76067BDFF396B3F4D7FAA5A7FDE_i_75_featurtn.jpg'><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-thumbnail' data-order='1'><!----><img src='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/D/B/1/5/3/DB15344D7BE512F32AC92F52502F63762155F564_i_75_featurtn.jpg' alt='Re-writable DVD drive' data-large='https://cc.cnetcontent.com/vcs/hp/inline-content/KV/D/B/1/5/3/DB15344D7BE512F32AC92F52502F63762155F564_i_75_featurtn.jpg'><!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='0'><!----><h3>Dropbox cloud storage</h3>Store and synchronize your content online with Dropbox. Get 25 GB of storage for one year to access, manage, and share your photos, music, and files from anywhere with Internet access.<!----></div><div class='ccs-cc-inline-feature-content ccs-cc-inline-feature-description' data-order='1'><!----><h3>Re-writable DVD drive</h3>Watch and write DVDs using the integrated optical drive.<!----></div></div></div></div><div id='specification-c67693' data-elementid='inline-content-specifications[hp]' data-context='{&quot;mobile&quot;:false}' data-ccs-cc-inline-jumplink='Specifications' class='ccs-cc-inline-section ccs-cc-inline-specifications' data-display-mode='expanded'><h2 class='ccs-cc-inline-section-title' data-ccs-jumplink-container='true'><a class='ccs-cc-inline-acc-header' title='Specifications' href='javascript:;' data-ccs-cc-inline-acc-id='specification-c67693' data-ccs-cc-inline-acc-state='expanded' aria-label='Specifications hides content'><span class='ccs-cc-inline-acc-icon'></span><span>Specifications</span></a></h2><div class='ccs-cc-inline-acc-content' data-ccs-cc-inline-acc-id='specification-c67693' style='display: block;'><table><tbody><tr class='ccs-cc-inline-specs-row'><th class='ccs-cc-inline-specification-attribute' scope='row'>Operating system</th><td>Windows 10 Home 64<sup><a id='ccs-f3inline-c67693' href='#ccs-ft3inline-c67693'>3</a></sup></td></tr><tr class='ccs-cc-inline-specs-row'><th class='ccs-cc-inline-specification-attribute' scope='row'>Memory</th><td>12 GB DDR4-2400 SDRAM (1 x 4 GB, 1 x 8 GB)</td></tr><tr class='ccs-cc-inline-specs-row'><th class='ccs-cc-inline-specification-attribute' scope='row'>Memory Note</th><td>Transfer rates up to 2400 MT/s.</td></tr><tr class='ccs-cc-inline-specs-row'><th class='ccs-cc-inline-specification-attribute' scope='row'>Memory and storage</th><td>12 GB memory<br>1 TB HD